name: #2-4 Wayo (The Four Fairies)
description:
This is a separate sub-collection of my Dream Dolls Collection. Nice to meet you "Wayo". 

Wayo, she is a fairy of the wind. On the day I dreamed that I saw you Her hair was like a green cloud. A cool breeze blows softly at me. The beauty and lines in her cloud-like hair were the swaying of the beautiful wind. It was very nice..
